               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gәṣṣәw, Lectionary for the week (fols. 3ra-22vb)&#xD;
- Barәkännä ʾәgziʾo… “Bless us, O Lord…” (Blessing prayer) (fols. 3ra-3vb)&#xD;
II) Ṣalota ˤǝṭan “Prayer of Incense” (fols.23ra-54va)&#xD;
- Prayer of Incense for Sunday (za-Sänbät) (fols. 40vb-52rb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Colophon.</summary>
